      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/hedge-funds-sell-software-stocks-as-ai-splits-tech-goldman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着人们越来越担心在人工智能热潮中谁会落后，对冲基金正在抛售软件类股票。]]></description>
