    <item>
      <title>经济学家称，一旦加拿大央行降息，债券价格将上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/economists-see-modest-bond-market-rally-after-bank-of-canada-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数经济学家表示，加拿大央行将于周三降低利率，并且他们认为，当首次降息最终实现时，政府债券将出现小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/economists-see-modest-bond-market-rally-after-bank-of-canada-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:58:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
