      <title>费城艺术学院因欠 5000 万美元市政债券而关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/philadelphia-arts-college-with-50-million-of-muni-debt-to-shut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费城艺术大学是一所私立大学，专门培养未来的动画师和舞蹈家，目前该校负有约 5000 万美元的市政债务，由于财务状况恶化，该校即将突然关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/philadelphia-arts-college-with-50-million-of-muni-debt-to-shut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>房主仍留在原地，Trex 押注房屋改造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/trex-bets-on-remodeling-as-homeowners-stay-put-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着夏季气温升高，Trex 的需求也随之飙升。这家户外装饰巨头正加倍投入 DIY 爱好者，押注装修热潮。首席执行官 Bryan Fairbanks 在“彭博市场”节目中与彭博社的 Katie Greifeld 讨论了他的前景。（更正嘉宾姓名。）（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/trex-bets-on-remodeling-as-homeowners-stay-put-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约证券交易所修复了导致股价下跌 99% 并引发交易暂停的问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/volatility-halts-hit-numerous-nyse-listed-stocks-in-error</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约证券交易所的技术故障导致多只股票错误交易暂停，包括 Chipotle Mexican Grill Inc. 和雅培实验室 (Abbott Laboratories) 的股票暂停交易，并且周一现货交易时段早些时候至少有两只股票出现异常交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/volatility-halts-hit-numerous-nyse-listed-stocks-in-error</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 14:08:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
